    rdfs:label "CDIF LocatorMapping building block" ;
    dct:abstract "Locates a variable's value(s) within a structured (hierarchical) dataset such as XML or JSON using a locator expression (XPath, JSONPath). Defines cdi:locator and cdif:formats_InstanceVariable. DDI-CDI LocatorMapping; used instead of column-index/text mappings for cdi:StructuredDataSet distributions."^^<https://www.w3.org/ns/iana/media-types/text/markdown> ;
