<bblocks://cdif.bbr.metadata.cdifDataType.cdifTabularTextDataSet> a skos:Concept,
        dcat:Dataset,
        bblocks:BBlock,
        bblocks:Schema ;
    rdfs:label "CDIF TabularTextDataSet building block" ;
    dct:abstract "Dataset-level physical layout of a delimited or fixed-width text dataset (CSV, TSV, fixed-width). A subclass of cdi:PhysicalDataSet carried on a schema:DataDownload distribution dual-typed cdi:TabularTextDataSet. Defines cdi:delimiter, cdi:hasHeader, cdi:headerRowCount, cdi:quoteCharacter, cdi:lineTerminator, cdi:isDelimited, cdi:isFixedWidth, cdi:skipRows, cdi:trim, cdi:tableDirection, cdi:textDirection (enumerations modeled as string+enum, matching the canonical ddicdiPhysicalDataSet), and the other DDI-CDI TabularTextDataSet attributes. Per-field mappings are cdifTextMapping."^^<https://www.w3.org/ns/iana/media-types/text/markdown> ;
    dct:created "2026-05-24T00:00:00+00:00"^^xsd:dateTime ;
    dct:description [ dct:format "text/html" ;
