<bblocks://cdif.bbr.metadata.cdifDataType.cdifReference> a skos:Concept,
        dcat:Dataset,
        bblocks:BBlock,
        bblocks:Schema ;
    rdfs:label "CDIF Relation" ;
    dct:abstract "A typed relation describing a link to another resource, combining the schema.org labeled-link surface (name, description, url) from labeledLink with the DCAT qualifiedRelation pattern. Carries a third @type (dcat:Relationship), a SKOS-typed role (dcat:hadRole), and the DCAT-canonical pointer to the related resource (dcterms:relation). Use as the target of a dcat:qualifiedRelation property, or wherever a typed link with an explicit role is needed. Defines properties: @type (must include 'schema:CreativeWork' and 'dcat:Relationship'), schema:name, schema:description, schema:url (required), dcat:hadRole (skos:Concept), dcterms:relation."^^<https://www.w3.org/ns/iana/media-types/text/markdown> ;
    dct:created "2026-05-16T00:00:00+00:00"^^xsd:dateTime ;
    dct:description [ dct:format "application/json" ;
